      <title>纳斯达克加强对中国内地及香港 IPO 投资者的审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/nasdaq-adds-scrutiny-of-investors-in-ipos-from-china-hk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，纳斯达克公司再次加强了对来自中国内地和香港的小型首次公开募股 (IPO) 的审查，以避免重演两年前几笔交易后的剧烈波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/nasdaq-adds-scrutiny-of-investors-in-ipos-from-china-hk</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 00:45:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币 ETF 首次在澳大利亚主要证券交易所上市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/bitcoin-btc-etf-lists-on-main-australian-stock-market-for-first-time</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一只投资比特币的交易所交易基金首次在澳大利亚主板上市，这是继今年在美国和香港推出类似基金之后的又一波上市潮。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/bitcoin-btc-etf-lists-on-main-australian-stock-market-for-first-time</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 00:44:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本百年老银行向世界发出长期高利率警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/norinchukin-sends-warning-to-world-on-higher-for-longer-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多年来，它最出名的身份是日本的 CLO 巨头——一家资产达 3570 亿美元的投资巨头，在利率处于最低水平的时代，对收益似乎有着永不满足的渴望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/norinchukin-sends-warning-to-world-on-higher-for-longer-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 00:25:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Olam 收购 Namoi Cotton 引起澳大利亚监管机构担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/olam-s-takeover-bid-for-namoi-cotton-concerns-australia-watchdog</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚监管机构担心，奥兰农业控股有限公司 (Olam Agri Holdings Ltd.) 拟以 1.44 亿澳元（9600 万美元）收购纳莫伊棉花有限公司 (Namoi Cotton Ltd.) 可能会减少轧棉服务之间的竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/olam-s-takeover-bid-for-namoi-cotton-concerns-australia-watchdog</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 00:22:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>期货成为马来西亚推高令吉汇率的首选工具</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/forwards-become-malaysia-s-favored-tool-for-boosting-the-ringgit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚央行越来越多地使用货币远期来支持林吉特，以减轻其外汇储备的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/forwards-become-malaysia-s-favored-tool-for-boosting-the-ringgit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 00:00:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
